{
  "texts": [
    "This alternative method offers several advantages.",
    "First, Selective-FD naturally adapts to heterogeneous models, eliminating the need for local models to share the same architecture.",
    "Second, Selective-FD largely reduces the communication overhead in comparison to FedAvg, since the size of knowledge is significantly smaller than the model.",
    "Third, Selective-FD provides a stronger privacy guarantee than FedAvg.",
    "The local models, which might contain encoded information from private datasets 22, remain inaccessible to other clients or the server."
  ]
}